(126, 'Отель А и Т', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Современность, стиль и </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">комфорт</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> отлично сочетаются в отеле А и Т, расположенном в юго-западной части </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">столицы</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. В шаговой </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">доступности</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; whi